item.title: CVE-2023-50774|2024-08-02T22:23:42.932Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20htmlresource%20plugin
item.description: A cross-site request forgery (CSRF) vulnerability in Jenkins HTMLResource Plugin 1.02 and earlier allows attackers to delete arbitrary files on the Jenkins controller file system.
